        <item>
            <title>中國景區流行智能外骨骼租借，行山都可出「外掛」更加輕鬆</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/ai-helps-hiking/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-helps-hiking</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/ai-helps-hiking/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 11:27:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[戀上山]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[行山]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303602</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中國多個旅遊景區近日推出智能外骨骼裝置租借服務，協助遊客減輕登山體力負擔。該設備由電力驅動，重量僅約 1.8 公斤，透過人工智能調節步伐，最高可降低 30% 體能消耗。現時深圳野生動物園、泰山及盧山等景區已提供服務，預計 2025 年內擴展至全國 25 個山嶽型景區。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303738" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h00-1.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/vlcsnap2025041619h01.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></a></p><h2>智能外骨骼提升登山體驗</h2><p>智能外骨骼裝置由腰部控制器及腿部支架組成，根據人體工學設計，搭載多模態感知系統，能識別行走及上下樓梯等動作，適時提供助力。續航達 3 至 5 小時，單次充電可行走約 14 公里。泰山文旅集團總經理王厚哲表示，外骨骼經深度學習可自動適應用家步伐，特別適合長者及體力較弱人士。有遊客接受訪問時表示，本來腳仍有點痛，使用後完全沒感覺了；另外亦有遊客指，外骨骼可自動抬腿，有種飄起來的感覺。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250326005172-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250326005172-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250326005172.jpg 1019w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20250326005171-260409?chdtv">中時新聞報</a></p><h2>景區科技化趨勢明顯</h2><p>除外骨骼裝置外，中國景區正積極引入其他智能裝置，如機械狗運送物資、導遊機械人及無人機外賣服務，提升遊客體驗。根據深圳市肯綮科技有限公司數據，全國逾 100 個景區有意引入外骨骼設備，數十個景區已進入測試階段。深圳野生動物園企劃部經理助理劉輝透露，免費試用一個多月已吸引數百人體驗。</p><h2>價格與普及前景</h2><p>租借費用方面，泰山景區外骨骼裝置定價為每 3 小時 80 元人民幣（約港幣 88 元），視乎使用地點或有折扣。肯綮科技產品總監楊工透露，智能外骨骼已量產，售價控制在 1 萬人民幣（約港幣 1.1 萬元）以內，未來有望進入個人市場，特別惠及行動不便人士。市場分析指，隨着技術成熟及成本降低，外骨骼設備或於 3 至 5 年內普及至更多旅遊及醫療場景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/043screenshot-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/043screenshot-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/043screenshot-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以調校不同力度，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhcVykxaalM&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%A4%BE">中國新聞社@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/046screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/046screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/046screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高可降低 30% 體能消耗，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhcVykxaalM&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%A4%BE">中國新聞社@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/018screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/018screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/018screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IhcVykxaalM&amp;ab_channel=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%A4%BE">中國新聞社@YouTube</a></p><h2></h2><h2>總結與未來展望</h2><p>智能外骨骼租借服務為中國景區旅遊注入科技元素，大幅提升長者及體弱遊客的登山體驗。隨着裝置量產及應用範圍擴大，預計 2025 年將有更多景區加入，推動智慧旅遊發展。惟成本與技術穩定性仍是普及關鍵，未來新聞或聚焦設備普及進度及用户反饋。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=600584">now</a>、<a href="https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20250326005171-260409?chdtv">中時新聞報</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/ai-helps-hiking/life-tech/%e6%88%80%e4%b8%8a%e5%b1%b1/">中國景區流行智能外骨骼租借，行山都可出「外掛」更加輕鬆</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
