        <item>
            <title>日廠推全新卡式帶錄音機，免電腦卡式帶轉成 MP3、並可直接播帶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kenko-tokina-kr019cr/mobile-music/musicplayers/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=kenko-tokina-kr019cr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kenko-tokina-kr019cr/mobile-music/musicplayers/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 10:06:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[隨身播放器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Kenko]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡式帶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡式帶轉換]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303628</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Kenko Tokina 即將推出「Kenko 便攜式卡式帶轉換播放器 KR-019CR」，讓用户可無需電腦輕鬆數碼化卡式帶，重温經典音色，配合 microSD 卡或 USB 記憶體即可轉換成 MP3，內置揚聲器亦可作卡式帶播放器使用，支援語音錄音及便攜設計，適合懷舊音樂愛好者。</p><h2>無須電腦數碼化卡式帶</h2><p>Kenko 便攜式卡式帶轉換播放器 KR-019CR 提供直觀操作，無需連接電腦即可將卡式帶轉換為 MP3 格式，支援 microSDHC（4GB 至 32GB）、microSDXC（64GB 至 128GB）或 USB 記憶體（最高 128GB）。用户只需插入儲存媒介，按下錄製鍵，即可將舊日音色保存為數碼檔案，過程簡單快捷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features01-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features01-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features01.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：Kenko-Tokina</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 USB、micro SD，圖片來源：Kenko-Tokina</p><h2>可直接播放卡式帶</h2><p>此播放器內置 76mm 揚聲器，支援 3W 輸出，可直接播放卡式帶，無需額外連接任何裝置。內置麥克風及 3.5mm 外置麥克風接口，方便錄音。機身設有手柄，方便攜帶或懸掛，尺寸約 49 x 149 x 245mm，重量僅 685g，輕巧耐用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features04-694x578.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features04-694x578.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features04-scaled.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：Kenko-Tokina</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身設有手柄，方便攜帶或懸掛，圖片來源：Kenko-Tokina</p><h2>靈活電源及兼容性</h2><p>KR-019CR 支援雙電源模式，包括 AC 電源（DC5V/1.5A）及 4 顆 2 號鹼性電池，電池續航力約 27 小時（音量 50% 時）。產品僅可使用普通卡式帶，不支援高性能或金屬卡式帶。耳機輸出為單聲道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features03-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features03-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features03.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：Kenko-Tokina</p><h2></h2><h2>售價及開售詳情</h2><p>KR-019CR 定價為 8,360 日元（約港幣 456 元），將於 4 月 18 日發售。</p><p>訂購連結：<a href="https://shop.kenko-tokina.co.jp/4961607446577">https://shop.kenko-tokina.co.jp/4961607446577</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kenko-tokina-kr019cr/mobile-music/musicplayers/">日廠推全新卡式帶錄音機，免電腦卡式帶轉成 MP3、並可直接播帶</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
